---
title: Italian Inspired Chorizo and Butter Bean Cassoulet with Green Beans, Pesto and Toasted Ciabatta
description: Originating from the south of France, cassoulets are typically slow-cooked and rich stews. Our Italian Inspired Chorizo and Butter Bean Cassoulet comes together a little faster for your table, with tomato, pesto and cheese bringing a taste of Italy.
